article_text:
On Wednesday, GOP House members will elect their 2016 speaker

Corcoran and others have a ‘manifesto’ in which they promise reform

Republican from Pasco County promises big changes to legislative process

article_metadata.news-keywords: Richard Corcoran, House speaker, Florida legislature, GOP, Pasco County
article_metadata.description: Poised to be one of the most powerful speakers of the House in recent history, Richard Corcoran says he wants to usher in reforms aimed at sharing power and curbing the influence of special interests.
article_metadata.title: Corcoran has legislative reforms in mind when he leads Florida House | Miami Herald
